snippet.textDisplay:
I think this was an huge eye opener for me, this whole show actually ...
Comming from an small town and all, I've never encountered (knowingly) people like the ones presented in this show or been talked about them in an educated or impartial way. It´s allways awful stories and rummors "oh you heard? Rosa's child is autistic, he doesn't talk, stay away from him, it's weird" ,"Maria's son is schizophrenic, he trashed the whole house, he is dangerous, stay away" it's allways" stay away! ". But I think this helps, as an outsider, like kind of a preview to open my mind about all these subjects and be more ready and comprehensive if I meet someone who decides to tell me that they are/identify in the groups talked about here.

So thanks for making my small world a little bit bigger.
